Clyde Cook (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clyde_Cook_(actor) 0 Clyde Wilfred Cook (16 December 1891 – 13 August 1984) was an Australian-born vaudevillian who went on to perform in Hollywood and whose career spanned the silent film era, talkies and television.
